<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>MemoTiles｜牆面懸掛佈置完全指南</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --red:#E53935;
  --red-dark:#C62828;
  --red-light:#FFEBEE;
  --red-mid:#FFCDD2;
  --black:#1A1A1A;
  --gray-dark:#424242;
  --gray:#757575;
  --gray-light:#BDBDBD;
  --gray-bg:#F5F5F5;
  --white:#FFFFFF;
  --border:#E0E0E0;
  --yellow:#FFF8E1;
  --yellow-border:#FFD54F;
  --green:#E8F5E9;
  --green-text:#2E7D32;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--white);color:var(--black);font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6}

/* ─ NAV ─ */
.topbar{background:var(--red);color:white;text-align:center;padding:8px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.5px}
.topbar span{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);padding:2px 10px;border-radius:3px;margin-left:8px;font-size:12px}
nav{background:white;border-bottom:2px solid var(--red);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
.nav-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:60px}
.nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.nav-logo-text{font-size:22px;font-weight:900;color:var(--black);letter-spacing:-0.5px}
.nav-logo-text b{color:var(--red)}
.nav-logo-badge{background:var(--red);color:white;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.5px}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:0;list-style:none}
.nav-links a{display:block;padding:0 16px;height:60px;line-height:60px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--gray-dark);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;transition:all .15s}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.act{color:var(--red);border-bottom-color:var(--red)}

/* ─ HERO ─ */
.hero{background:var(--gray-bg);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0}
.hero-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 480px;gap:48px;align-items:center}
.hero-kicker{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--red-light);color:var(--red);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:3px;margin-bottom:16px;letter-spacing:.5px}
.hero-kicker::before{content:'▶';font-size:9px}
.hero-h1{font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,42px);font-weight:900;color:var(--black);line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:16px}
.hero-h1 em{color:var(--red);font-style:normal}
.hero-desc{font-size:15px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:24px}
.hero-specs{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:28px}
.spec-chip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:white;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--black)}
.spec-chip .chip-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:2px}
.chip-s{background:#E57373}
.chip-r{background:#EF5350}
.chip-g{background:#B71C1C}
.hero-badges{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-badge{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);font-weight:500}
.hero-badge::before{content:'✓';color:var(--green-text);font-weight:900}

/* Hero product visual */
.hero-visual{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px}
.hv-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray);letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.hv-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:10px;justify-content:center}
/* 1cm = 13px */
.hv-20s{width:130px;height:130px;border-radius:4px;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.15);position:relative}
.hv-20r{width:130px;height:195px;border-radius:4px;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.15);position:relative}
.hv-30s{width:195px;height:195px;border-radius:4px;box-shadow:0 3px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.15);position:relative}
.hv-20s::after,.hv-20r::after,.hv-30s::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,.25),transparent 60%)}
.col-s{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF9A9A,#E53935)}
.col-r{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF5350,#B71C1C)}
.col-g{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF9A9A 0%,#E53935 50%,#B71C1C 100%)}
.col-sm{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#FFCDD2,#EF9A9A)}
.col-rm{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#FFCDD2,#EF5350)}
.hv-label{text-align:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray);margin-top:6px;letter-spacing:.5px}

/* ─ PAGE LAYOUT ─ */
.page-max{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}

/* ─ SECTION HEADER ─ */
.sec{padding:56px 0}
.sec-alt{background:var(--gray-bg)}
.sec-hd{margin-bottom:32px}
.sec-hd-inner{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;padding-bottom:14px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--black);margin-bottom:4px}
.sec-hd h2{font-size:clamp(20px,2.5vw,26px);font-weight:900;color:var(--black)}
.sec-hd h2 em{color:var(--red);font-style:normal}
.sec-tag{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--red);letter-spacing:1px}
.sec-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray);margin-top:6px}
.sec-hd-line{height:3px;background:var(--red);width:48px}

/* ─ SIZE CARDS ─ */
.size-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.sz-card{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s,border-color .2s}
.sz-card:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(229,57,53,.12);border-color:var(--red-mid)}
.sz-card-top{padding:28px 24px 20px;background:var(--gray-bg);text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.sz-visual-wrap{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-end;height:130px;margin-bottom:16px}
/* 1cm = 11px */
.sv-20x20{width:110px;height:110px;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF9A9A,#E53935);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(229,57,53,.3)}
.sv-20x30{width:110px;height:165px;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF5350,#B71C1C);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(183,28,28,.3)}
.sv-30x30{width:165px;height:165px;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#E53935,#7F0000);box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(127,0,0,.3)}
.sz-dim{font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:var(--black);margin-bottom:2px}
.sz-nick{display:inline-block;background:var(--red-light);color:var(--red);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.5px}
.sz-card-body{padding:20px 24px}
.sz-card-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-dark);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:14px}
.sz-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px}
.sz-tag{background:var(--gray-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);font-size:11px;color:var(--gray-dark);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;font-weight:500}
.sz-best{background:var(--red-light);border-color:var(--red-mid);color:var(--red)}

/* ─ LAYOUT CARDS ─ */
.layout-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:16px}
.lc{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s,border-color .2s}
.lc:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.1);border-color:var(--gray-light)}
.lc-vis{height:240px;background:var(--gray-bg);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;position:relative;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.lc-num{position:absolute;top:10px;left:14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:900;color:var(--gray-light);letter-spacing:1px}
.lc-hot{position:absolute;top:10px;right:14px;background:var(--red);color:white;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.5px}
.lc-new{position:absolute;top:10px;right:14px;background:var(--black);color:white;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.5px}

/* tiles inside layout cards: 1cm = 8px */
.t{border-radius:3px;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.18)}
.t::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:3px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,.2),transparent 55%)}
.ts{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF9A9A,#E53935)}
.tr{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF5350,#B71C1C)}
.tg{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#E53935,#7F0000)}
.tsm{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#FFCDD2,#EF9A9A)}
.trm{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#FFCDD2,#EF5350)}
.tgm{background:linear-gradient(145deg,#EF9A9A,#C62828)}
/* 20×20=40px  20×30=40×60px  30×30=60×60px */
.p-ss{width:40px;height:40px}
.p-sr{width:40px;height:60px}
.p-sq{width:60px;height:60px}
/* large versions for featured */
.P-ss{width:56px;height:56px}
.P-sr{width:56px;height:84px}
.P-sq{width:84px;height:84px}
/* xl */
.X-ss{width:72px;height:72px}
.X-sr{width:72px;height:108px}
.X-sq{width:108px;height:108px}
.row{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-end}
.col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.grid2c{display:grid;gap:8px}

.lc-body{padding:16px 20px 20px}
.lc-spec-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px}
.lc-spec-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:2px}
.dot-s{background:var(--red)}
.dot-r{background:#C62828}
.dot-g{background:#7F0000}
.lc-name{font-size:17px;font-weight:900;color:var(--black);margin-bottom:6px}
.lc-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:12px}
.lc-meta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.lc-chip{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px}
.chip-red{background:var(--red-light);color:var(--red)}
.chip-black{background:var(--gray-bg);color:var(--gray-dark)}
.chip-green{background:var(--green);color:var(--green-text)}

/* ─ SCENE SECTION ─ */
.scene-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:16px}
.sc-card{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;transition:box-shadow .2s}
.sc-card:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.09)}
.sc-top{background:var(--red);padding:20px 22px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.sc-icon{font-size:28px}
.sc-title-wrap{}
.sc-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:white;margin-bottom:2px}
.sc-place{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.5px}
.sc-body{padding:18px 22px}
.sc-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-dark);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:14px}
.sc-recipes{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.sc-recipe{background:var(--gray-bg);border-left:3px solid var(--red);padding:8px 12px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;font-size:12px;color:var(--gray-dark);line-height:1.5}
.sc-recipe b{color:var(--black);font-weight:700}

/* ─ COMBO TABLE ─ */
.combo-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden}
.combo-table thead tr{background:var(--black)}
.combo-table thead th{padding:12px 16px;text-align:left;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:white;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.combo-table tbody tr{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background .15s}
.combo-table tbody tr:hover{background:var(--red-light)}
.combo-table tbody tr:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.combo-table td{padding:14px 16px;font-size:14px;color:var(--gray-dark);vertical-align:middle}
.combo-table td:first-child{font-weight:900;color:var(--black);font-size:15px}
.combo-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap}
.ct-hot{background:var(--red);color:white}
.ct-rec{background:var(--red-light);color:var(--red)}
.ct-new{background:var(--black);color:white}
.ct-gift{background:#FFF8E1;color:#F57F17;border:1px solid #FFD54F}

/* ─ MARKETING COPY ─ */
.mkt-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:16px}
.mk{background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden}
.mk-head{background:var(--black);padding:14px 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.mk-channel{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:white;letter-spacing:.5px}
.mk-platform{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
.mk-body-wrap{padding:20px}
.mk-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:var(--black);margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.3}
.mk-copy{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-dark);line-height:1.85;white-space:pre-line;background:var(--gray-bg);padding:14px 16px;border-radius:4px;border-left:3px solid var(--red)}

/* ─ TIPS ─ */
.tips-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:white}
.tip-row{display:flex;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.tip-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.tip-num-col{width:64px;background:var(--red);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.tip-num{font-size:24px;font-weight:900;color:white}
.tip-content{padding:18px 22px;flex:1}
.tip-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:900;color:var(--black);margin-bottom:5px}
.tip-text{font-size:13px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7}

/* ─ NOTICE BOX ─ */
.notice{background:var(--yellow);border:1.5px solid var(--yellow-border);border-radius:6px;padding:16px 20px;display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:24px}
.notice-icon{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.notice-text{font-size:13px;color:#4E342E;line-height:1.75}
.notice-text b{color:var(--black);font-weight:700}

/* ─ LEGEND BAR ─ */
.legend{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:12px 16px;background:white;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:20px}
.legend-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray);letter-spacing:.5px;flex-shrink:0}
.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--black)}
.leg-box{border-radius:2px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}

/* ─ CTA BLOCK ─ */
.cta-block{background:var(--red);border-radius:6px;padding:48px 48px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:32px;align-items:center}
.cta-left h2{font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:900;color:white;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.2}
.cta-left p{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);line-height:1.7}
.cta-right{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;flex-shrink:0}
.btn-white{background:white;color:var(--red);font-size:14px;font-weight:900;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;border:none;letter-spacing:.5px;transition:background .15s;white-space:nowrap}
.btn-white:hover{background:#FFEBEE}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;color:white;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.5);letter-spacing:.5px;white-space:nowrap}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:white}

/* ─ FOOTER ─ */
footer{background:var(--black);color:white;padding:32px 24px;margin-top:0}
.footer-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
.footer-brand{font-size:18px;font-weight:900;color:white}
.footer-brand span{color:var(--red)}
.footer-info{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-align:right}

/* ─ REVEAL ─ */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity .5s ease,transform .5s ease}
.reveal.on{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}

/* ─ BREADCRUMB ─ */
.breadcrumb{padding:10px 0;font-size:12px;color:var(--gray);display:flex;gap:5px;align-items:center}
.breadcrumb a{color:var(--gray);text-decoration:none}
.breadcrumb a:hover{color:var(--red)}
.breadcrumb span{color:var(--gray-light)}

@media(max-width:800px){
  .hero-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:28px 16px}
  .hero-visual{display:none}
  .size-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .cta-block{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  nav .nav-links{display:none}
  .page-max{padding:0 16px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOPBAR -->
<div class="topbar">🎉 多件優惠進行中！買 3 件享 9 折，買 6 件享 85 折 <span>立即選購 →</span></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <div class="nav-logo">
      <div class="nav-logo-text">Memo<b>Tiles</b></div>
      <div class="nav-logo-badge">客製化照片磚</div>
    </div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#sizes" class="act">尺寸介紹</a></li>
      <li><a href="#layouts">懸掛方式</a></li>
      <li><a href="#scenes">場景應用</a></li>
      <li><a href="#combos">套組方案</a></li>
      <li><a href="#marketing">行銷話術</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-kicker">牆面懸掛完全指南</div>
      <h1 class="hero-h1">三種尺寸<br><em>打造你專屬的照片牆</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">MemoTiles 提供 20×20、20×30、30×30 cm 三種規格<br>免打洞、可重複黏貼，讓每一面牆都成為你的生活故事</p>
      <div class="hero-specs">
        <div class="spec-chip"><div class="chip-dot chip-s"></div>20×20 cm</div>
        <div class="spec-chip"><div class="chip-dot chip-r"></div>20×30 cm</div>
        <div class="spec-chip"><div class="chip-dot chip-g"></div>30×30 cm</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-badges">
        <div class="hero-badge">免打洞，不傷牆面</div>
        <div class="hero-badge">可重複移位</div>
        <div class="hero-badge">租屋族適用</div>
        <div class="hero-badge">7 天到貨</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hv-title">產品實際比例示意圖</div>
      <div class="hv-row">
        <div>
          <div class="hv-20s col-s"></div>
          <div class="hv-label">20×20</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="hv-20r col-r"></div>
          <div class="hv-label">20×30</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="hv-30s col-g"></div>
          <div class="hv-label">30×30</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--yellow);border:1px solid var(--yellow-border);border-radius:4px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;color:#4E342E;line-height:1.6;margin-top:8px">
        📐 <b>以上示意圖依實際比例繪製</b><br>三種尺寸可自由搭配組合使用
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SIZES SECTION -->
<section id="sizes" class="sec">
  <div class="page-max">
    <div class="sec-hd reveal">
      <div class="sec-hd-inner">
        <h2>三種尺寸 <em>完整介紹</em></h2>
        <div class="sec-tag">PRODUCT SIZES</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sec-hd-line"></div>
      <p class="sec-sub">了解每種尺寸的特性，選對規格讓佈置效果加倍！</p>
    </div>
    <div class="notice reveal">
      <div class="notice-icon">💡</div>
      <div class="notice-text"><b>選購小提示：</b>不確定要幾片？先從 4 片入門組開始嘗試。MemoTiles 可無限擴充，滿意後再追加購買，片片相容、輕鬆拼接。</div>
